《星际争霸》系列在商业上取得了重大的成功，在发售当年便在全球售出逾150万份拷贝<ref name="1998sales"/>，更荣膺当年[[电子游戏销量排行列表#PC|最畅销电脑游戏]]称号。在之后的十年里，星际争霸共售出约950万份拷贝，其中有450万份销往了韩国<ref name="usatoday">{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2007-05-21-starcraft2-peek_N.htm |title=South Korean gamers get a sneak peek at 'StarCraft II' |accessdate=2008-08-26 |author=Olsen, Kelly |date=2007-05-21 |publisher=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |archive-date=2008-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080929124905/http://www.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2007-05-21-starcraft2-peek_N.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。据[[暴雪娱乐|暴雪]]的数据统计显示，《星际争霸》上市之后，[[战网|战网]]的多人游戏业务增长了800%<ref>{{cite web|title=Blizzard's Battle.net Remains Largest Online Game Service in the World; Battle.net Dominates Online Gaming Industry With 2.1 Million Active Users; Korea Becomes World's No. 1 Market |publisher=Business Wire |date=1999-02-04 |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0EIN/is_1999_Feb_4/ai_53706429 |accessdate=2008-07-20 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120529182015/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0EIN/is_1999_Feb_4/ai_53706429/ |archivedate=2012-05-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 。至今，《星际争霸》仍然是全世界最畅销的在线游戏之一<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2008-09-06|url=http://www.edge-online.com/magazine/retrospective-ten-years-starcraft|title=RETROSPECTIVE: Ten Years of StarCraft |publisher=''Edge''|date=2008-04-01 }}</ref><ref name="fans">{{cite web|author=Rossignol, Jim |title=Sex, Fame and PC Baangs: How the Orient plays host to PC gaming's strangest culture |publisher=PC Gamer UK |date=2005-04-01 |url=http://rossignol.cream.org/?p=284 |accessdate=2008-08-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060202060802/http://rossignol.cream.org/?p=284 |archivedate=2006-02-02 }}</ref><ref name="thenewyorktimes">{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/05/21/technology/21warcraft.html |title=To the Glee of South Korean Fans, a Game's Sequel Is Announced |accessdate=2008-08-26 |author=Schiesel, Seth |date=2007-05-21 |publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124031837/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/05/21/technology/21warcraft.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《星际争霸》发售之后在韩国迅速蹿红，有力地拉动了当地的[[电子竞技|电子竞技]]产业<ref>{{cite web| author = Ki-tae, Kim| title = Will ''StarCraft'' Survive Next 10 Years?| publisher = The Korea Times| date = 2005-03-20| url = http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/news_view.asp?newsIdx=2582126| accessdate = 2008-08-26| archive-date = 2007-09-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927191427/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/news_view.asp?newsIdx=2582126| dead-url = no}}</ref> 。在韩国，电子竞技高手们拥有众多粉丝，超过三家电视台专门从事《星际争霸》电子竞技的转播工作<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2008-08-26 |url=http://techrepublic-cnet.com.com/South+Korea+leads+the+way/2009-1034_3-5261393.html |title=Broadband: South Korea leads the way |publisher=CNET |date=2004-07-28 |author=Borland, John; Kanellos, Michael |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120717223935/http://news.cnet.com/South-Korea-leads-the-way/2009-1034_3-5261393.html |archivedate=2012-07-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 。《星际争霸》获得的年度游戏奖项数不胜数<ref name="awardss">{{cite web|title=Developer Awards |publisher=[[Blizzard_Entertainment|Blizzard Entertainment]] |date=2006-01-01 |url=http://www.blizzard.com/inblizz/awards.shtml |accessdate=2006-08-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060814090829/http://www.blizzard.com/inblizz/awards.shtml |archivedate=2006-08-14 }}</ref> ，被认为是有史以来最优秀的即时战略游戏之一<ref name="GspotAward">{{cite web|url=http://uk.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/greatestgames/starcraft.html |title=The Greatest Games of All Time |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |year=1998 |accessdate=2008-09-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060705173935/http://uk.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/greatestgames/starcraft.html |archivedate=2006-07-05 }}</ref>，并以其风格迥异但是平衡性极强的种族设定而闻名。<ref name="popular">{{cite web | title = IGN's Top 100 Games | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2005-01-01 | url = http://top100.ign.com/2005/001-010.html | accessdate = 2006-08-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6YQvH6xHh?url=http://top100.ign.com/2005/001-010.html | archivedate = 2015年5月11日 | df =  }}</ref>

虽然《星际争霸》的前两个资料片Insurrection和Retribution普遍评价不高<ref name="ins GR"/>，但[[母巢之战|母巢之战]]最终取得了巨大的成功，并在[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]的总评中得到了96%<ref name="GR75249"/>的高分。在{{le|PC Zone}}杂志简短而不失溢美的评论中，作者认为其品质足以安慰那些因暴雪招牌式的跳票而苦苦等待的玩家，并高度赞扬了游戏的过场动画，称其与游戏浑然一体，不显突兀<ref name="PCZone">{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=3469|title=PC review: ''StarCraft: Brood War''|work=PC Zone|publisher=ComputerAndVideoGames.com|author=Emery, Daniel|date=2001-08-12|accessdate=2008-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080403171122/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=3469|archive-date=2008-04-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]评论说母巢之战提升了游戏的核心体验而不失其原汁原味<ref name="IGNBW">{{cite web|url=http://uk.mac.ign.com/articles/361/361674p1.html|title=''StarCraft: Brood War'' review|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|author=Chen, Jeffrey|date=June 7, 2002|accessdate=2007-11-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64zFcr6GS?url=http://uk.mac.ign.com/articles/361/361674p1.html|archive-date=2012-01-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]认为，暴雪在母巢之战倾注了大量心血，犹如对待一款全新的游戏<ref name="GameSpot review">{{cite web|url=http://uk.gamespot.com/pc/strategy/starcraftexpansionsetbw/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=tabs&tag=tabs;reviews |title=''StarCraft: Brood War'' for PC review |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |author=Saggeran, Vik |date=1998-12-23 |accessdate=2007-11-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207031943/http://uk.gamespot.com/pc/strategy/starcraftexpansionsetbw/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=tabs&tag=tabs%3Breviews |archivedate=2009-02-07 }}</ref>。

